How to create a python script on your deserver:

1. Type “ vi .<script-name> “
2. Type “#!/usr/bin/env python3” on top of list for python
3. Type code in vi 
4.  An alternative to copy past python code is to use “cat > <script-name.py>” to avoid indentation issues
5. :wq! # to write and quit script
6.  Chmod +x <script-name> # creates an executable 
7.  ./<script-name> # to run file 


