How to create a bash script on your deserver

0. ctrl+c -> :wq! (To quit)
0. Type s to insert text
0. Hjkl (left, up, down right)

1. Type “vi <script-name>”
    1. You can change your name to
2. Type code into text editor (Vim/nano)
3. Move file to bin folder “mv <script-name> bin/ 
    1. Create a bin folder if you don’t have one “mkdir bin”
4. Make your file an executable. “Chmod +x <script-name>”
